User Stories Sprint 1
Randy Alfonso
9-10-2020

Rating Books

As a user of the online shopping market, I would like to have the
ability to rate books, so other users can have a rough idea of the 
quality of the products they see available.

Conditions of Satisfaction

Give rating of product on the market
Rating should be between 0 and a number desired by the client
Ratings should be attached to the product
All ratings should be average numbers, after + all ratings / by # of ratings
Ratings should be visible in product information
